    "text": [
        "Dear Mr.Loyds,",
        "I am writing this letter to inform you that I would not be able to continue the digital marketing course, which I joined on the 1st of April 2020.",
        "Although, I learned many new Digital skills through such course and enjoyed it immensely. As I mentioned in the  Course form, I work full-time in an IT company. Until now, it was easy to manage the course along with the office work.",
        "However, my company just signed a USA based project, and they chose a team of five people, including me, is being to send the  USA to negotiate some terms and conditions. I will probably be out of the country for a couple of weeks. Initially, I thought to continue the course online, but now it seems not possible to me as per schedule will be.",
        "Could you please permit me to continue the course after returning to India? Otherwise, please reserve a seat for me in the next cohort in September because this course is highly beneficial for my career.",
